    "# Early Detection of Type 2 Diabetes Using Machine Learning, Explainable AI, Ontology, Calibration and Dashboard Visualization\n",
    "\n",
    "**Project Overview**\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook implements a full diabetes screening pipeline using \n",
    "NHANES 2015–2018 survey data. The pipeline addresses four gaps \n",
    "identified in the existing literature:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Calibration** — probability outputs are assessed and corrected\n",
    "2. **Threshold Optimisation** — screening threshold selected clinically\n",
    "3. **Robustness** — results validated across 10 random seeds\n",
    "4. **Contradiction Detection** — clinical rule layer flags conflicts\n",
    "\n",
    "**Models evaluated:** Logistic Regression, Random Forest, \n",
    "XGBoost (default + tuned), Neural Network (MLP)  \n",
    "**Explainability:** SHAP and LIME  \n",
    "**Primary model:** Tuned XGBoost (GridSearchCV optimised)  \n",
    "**Dataset:** NHANES 2015–2018 | 10,168 adults | 15.5% diabetic"
   ]
  },
